{"body": "WDYT?\r\n\r\n```markdown\r\n*   Fix issue that raises `NameError` when overriding the `accepts_nested_attributes` in child classes.\r\n\r\n    Before:\r\n\r\n        class Shared::Person < ActiveRecord::Base\r\n          has_one :address\r\n\r\n          accepts_nested_attributes :address, :reject_if => :all_blank\r\n        end\r\n\r\n        class Person < Shared::Person\r\n          accepts_nested_attributes :address\r\n        end\r\n        \r\n        Person\r\n        #=> NameError: method `address_attributes=' not defined in Person\r\n\r\n    After:\r\n\r\n        Person\r\n        #=> Person(id: integer, ...)\r\n\r\n    Fixes #8131.\r\n\r\n    *Gabriel Sobrinho, Ricardo Henrique*\r\n```", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/10158845", "created_at": "2012-11-07T18:16:35Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/8138#issuecomment-10158845", "updated_at": "2012-11-07T18:16:35Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 8138, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/rafaelfranca", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F2c7b84fa30f0cea96a90729afe2970a0.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/received_events", "gravatar_id": "0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "rafaelfranca", "type": "User", "id": 47848, "followers_url": "https://api.g